title: thread 'rustc' panicked at 'index out of bounds: the len is 681 but the index is 682'

body:
### Code Still working out how to get rid of this and find a minimal replicating code example. The backtrace however, contains some useful information like "index out of bounds", for those who knows the implementation of the compiler.
